{"tid":2143503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蚑那狗欺凌香港同學對策三步曲","createTime":"2020-08-07T06:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T09:34:16.000Z","uid":48234,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3981028e643d80d32845f2255a40393843538b5d","tid":2143503,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T06:33:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">1: 預防</span></span><br />\n所有香港學生家長定期問自己小朋友有冇俾蚑那同學欺凌<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">2: 起底</span></span><br />\n如果真係出現被欺凌，請香港學生/家長盡力起底，最好有相、名、出沒地點<br />\n有錢嘅，可以搵定打手<br />\n窮嘅，可以放欺凌者資料上網/某啲解決問題專用嘅telegram group<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">3: 解決</span></span><br />\n埋伏欺凌者，然後解決問題<br />\n有錢嘅，搵到打手就可以幫你<br />\n窮嘅，你只能等待義務制裁者幫你"},{"pid":"131243b59e0146bdcd4c782116e6662b6dd827bb","tid":2143503,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T06:38:54.000Z","msg":"被欺凌好多小學生嚟<br />\n講個字頭都驚到唔敢出聲啦<br />\n仲要求佢地主動求助好難"},{"pid":"7efb8d42282beb2124b1d189b35d28757391796d","tid":2143503,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"131243b59e0146bdcd4c782116e6662b6dd827bb","tid":2143503,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T06:38:54.000Z","msg":"被欺凌好多小學生嚟<br />\n講個字頭都驚到唔敢出聲啦<br />\n仲要求佢地主動求助好難"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:04:03.000Z","msg":"所以要由家長做起<br />\n要確保欺凌者受到應得制裁<br />\n嚴重嘅，就算死刑制裁都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863224256c0b74b161dd153ad53f36b8c39f189e","tid":2143503,"uid":111372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:39:43.000Z","msg":"最好都係自己人組織下，FD底互照"},{"pid":"6595dcbd09be78ec071953a59c6517e60592cd30","tid":2143503,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:41:30.000Z","msg":"對班支那狗俾教訓唔得"},{"pid":"f1cac092f6a1b83e70d7624ac28cc0b6bd790d2a","tid":2143503,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"